	     <tr><td id="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top"><a id="sj" href="/db/item.html?item=4105&amp;mid=97717996229067">Use of Lances?!?--Notes on this</a> <a id="fs8" href="/db/item.html?item=4105&amp;mid=97717996229067#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11" /></a>
